Introduction

U.SSO Girl was a children girl group under Kids Planet (ON1 Entertainment and 4D Label) and KITORY. They debuted on 7th November 2017. They have 9 former members, including NewJeans' Hyein and BABYMONSTER's Rora. The girls are also active as models.
